Package model

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AtomicExpense
    An interface for the atomic expense elements that make up the list of expenses.
    Bill
    An concrete class of the Atomic Expense class.
    Date
    A class to keep track of the due dates for expenses
    ExpenseFactory
    The Expense Factory is a design pattern to create concrete expenses at runtime
    ExpenseList
    The Expense List class stores the relevant data for the finance tracking program.
    Purchase
    An concrete class of the Atomic Expense class.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    ExpenseType
    The Expense Type enumerated class describes the types of expenses, either one time "purchases" or recurring cost "bills"
    PaymentInterval
    The interval of payment for recurring bills
    PaymentType
    The type of payment method used
